{"type": "article", "id": 2779, "title": "Tea Egg 泡茶棒", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-11T07:50:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052325454R8xueIz7cFGZSCT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦的设计工作室 Made by Makers 为丹麦设计品牌 Normann Copenhagen 设计了一款名为“ Tea Egg ”的泡茶棒，贴心的颜色设计可以随着心情搭配不同种类的茶。泡茶棒独特的球体设计，均匀分布着圆形小洞，不仅让泡茶更快速，洗净后的收纳也很通风。在造型上纤细、轻巧的长柄设计，让泡茶棒同时也是搅拌棒，加点牛奶和蜂蜜，更简单地跟茶融合在一起。用户只需取适量的茶叶放进球体，一冲入热水马上就从小洞里散出漂亮的茶色。定价 14 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.connox.com/categories/cooking/tea/normann-copenhagen-tea-egg.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232543DofUL6cymsaIpQiH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232543PHMOE6LwxGURYb8X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232543UOINT43BY9KJhkjQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232544zriDlNFvOdU9jEAc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232544xzvVAtITHUKCkQp6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}